Head.
Frons, vertex and labrum brown, labial and maxillary palpi dark brown or black. Antenna yellowishbrown, apical antennomere darker (
Fig. 165
), length of second to third antennomere 0.58–0.64 (mean: 0.60), and length of third to fourth antennomere 0.63–0.71 (mean: 0.67) (
Fig. 167
). Eyes large with short interocular distance (
Fig. 165
), width of eye to interocular distance 0.42–0.52 (mean: 0.49).
